NG0589:1127: mtshon cha'i rgyal po drug gnyis dgod //
NG0589:1128: phyi rim bcu drug kha gnon stobs //
NG0589:1129: tha ma spu gri ldan par bya //
NG0589:1130: drag po'i mthu stobs ya la sdu //
NG0589:1131: 'khor lo me dbal mtshon chen gyis //
NG0589:1132: zhing bcu ma lus brtan nas bsreg / de yi yon tan dpag med la //
NG0589:1133: byin brlabs mthu stobs gtan dpag med //
NG0589:1134: ye shes 'khor lo brtan pa sbyin //
NG0589:1135: dag pa'i zhing las sna tshogs las //
NG0589:1136: brgyad dang bcu gnyis la sogs pa //
NG0589:1137: las kyi rim pa bsam dpag yas //
NG0589:1138: rtsa ba bzhi la du mar 'gyur //
NG0589:1139: 'byung bzhi gnas pa'i mtshon cha la //
NG0589:1140: byin rlobs du ma skabs kyis te //
NG0589:1141: me dpal sngags dang 'khor lo mtshon //
NG0589:1142: gcod pa'i sreg pa drag po'i las //
NG0589:1143: 'joms byed ya ma'i zhing khams nas //
NG0589:1144: 'joms byed drag po zhe sdang mchog / 'bar ba dug gi dum bur bsdus //
NG0589:1146: sbyor ba'i rtsa la spel zhing sdud //
NG0589:1147: dbang sdud 'khor lo 'bar ba'i mchog / khrag 'thung 'bar ba'i lus la gzud //
NG0589:1148: sna tshogs dug gi khu bas byug / rten 'brel stobs dang nus pa yi //
NG0589:1149: myos pa'i rdzas kyi du bas bdug / 'khor lo'i nus tshad ngar dang ldan //
NG0589:1150: dbus dang mtshams kyi 'brub gnas su //
NG0589:1151: rgyu rkyen drug la sogs pa yi //
NG0589:1152: 'dod pa'i dri ma kun bsdus la //
NG0589:1153: ma lus kun gyi sdig pa sgo //
NG0589:1154: nye bar gyur pa'i yan lag yin //
NG0589:1155: zhing bcu ma lus rten la bstim //
NG0589:1156: thugs kyi rgyun gyis mthu stobs ldan //
NG0589:1157: bsgrub bya gang dmigs cig la bsdu //
NG0589:1158: srog sdud snying po rten can no //
NG0589:1159: tshe rten tshe gnas thig ler gzhug / drag po
NG0589:1160: stobs dang mthu dbang 'phrog / mkha' 'gro dbang phyug
NG0589:1161: lto bar gzhug / mi 'gyur brtan pa'i phyag rgya
NG0589:1162: yin // brnag pa kun gyis snying po mchog / gcod pa'i 'khor lo me dbal yin //
NG0589:1163: dngas ma tshe gnas thig le bstim //
NG0589:1164: 'byung ba bzhi yi mdangs bsdus la //
NG0589:1165: snyigs ma rjen shul sha za rol //
NG0589:1166: de dag po dag snying po'i bdag / 'jam dpal thugs kyi snying po 'di //
NG0589:1167: stong pa'i ye shes dbus nyid dngos //
NG0589:1168: gsal ba'i ye shes bzhi ldan te //
NG0589:1169: las dang 'bras bu smin pa'i mchog / bde ba'i mtshon cha 'khor lo can //
NG0589:1170: yul du snang ba gzugs brnyan yin //
NG0589:1171: sgyu ma'i bsti gnas dbang po'i yul //
NG0589:1172: de la stobs kyi las dang mjug khams gsum sreg
NG0589:1177: sprul pa rang byung 'od shar zhing *//
NG0589:1178: dus gsum rgyal bas bka' brgyud pa'i //
NG0589:1180: bka' yi bdud sgo dngos grub gter //
NG0589:1181: mtshon chen 'khor lor gter gyi mchog / thabs rnams ldan dang mi ldan pas //
NG0589:1182: bya ba kun grub rlag par 'gyur //
NG0589:1183: gang zhig drug gi yan lag lus //
NG0589:1184: smin cing rkyen dang ldan pa la //
NG0589:1187: rngam pa'i gzer gyis 'bru btus te //
NG0589:1188: rtsa ba spu gri 'khor lor bcas //
NG0589:1189: 'khrugs byed kun gyi mtshon cha ste //
NG0589:1190: ha la nag po bdud srin gshed //
NG0589:1191: srag sgo gnyis kyi la nas ston //
NG0589:1192: 'byung ba gnas kyi khams su bstim //
NG0589:1193: srog rten dwangs ma gnas su bsdu //
NG0589:1194: ya la phab la thig ler gzhug / rdo rje dregs pa gcod pa yi //
NG0589:1195: srog ldan khams gsum ma lus pa'i //
NG0589:1196: gshin rje rgyal po srog gi gshed //
NG0589:1197: srog lus 'bral par shar gnyer bas //
NG0589:1198: gshed ces bya ba las gnyer yin //
NG0589:1199: 'byung ba bzhi dang rten sa bzhi //
NG0589:1200: bla gnas bzhi 'joms nyi ma'i las //
NG0589:1201: zhing bcu sreg pa'i nyi ma yin //
NG0589:1202: ye shes 'od ldan bskul ba'i rkyen //
NG0589:1203: nyon mongs lam gol las kyi mchog / phra mo rgyun gcod mtshon cha'i las //
NG0589:1204: de yi bsgrub bya gang yin la //
NG0589:1205: mtshan nam nyi ma bzhi bzhir bsgrub //
NG0589:1206: de phyir nyi ma bzhi zhes bya //
NG0589:1207: nyi ma las kyi rim pa ni //
NG0589:1208: gnas pa bsgrub bya'i srog rten la //
NG0589:1209: gnas pa'i snying po khams chen bzhi //
NG0589:1211: sa dang me yi snying po blang *//
NG0589:1212: g.yeng dang blan pa'i rtsa sgo ru //
NG0589:1213: rlung dang chu yi snying po brtag / rten gsum dbugs kyi srog shing la //
NG0589:1214: rten dang sdud pa'i snying po bzung *//
NG0589:1215: rtsa bran brgyad dang sul bzhi la //
NG0589:1216: bcu gnyis gzer gyi snying po gnas //
NG0589:1217: bdud bzhi snying gzer dngas ma gnas rtsa //
NG0589:1219: rtsa yi sbyor ba brgya dang gcig / drug gnyis yan lag sbyor ba yin //
NG0589:1220: rnal zlog dkrug mchongs 'dros thabs brgyad //
NG0589:1221: drug gnyis 'pho ba'i las gnyis brtags //
NG0589:1222: dril ba'i 'khor lo mtsho chen tshul //
NG0589:1223: brgyab pas yang tog bdud kyi stobs //
NG0589:1224: drag po za byed myos pa'i sngags //
NG0589:1225: ho pan srog 'dzin sbyor ba brgyad //
NG0589:1226: dug gsum srog 'joms tshe gnas bstim //
NG0589:1227: spogs pa rang gzir khugs dang gso //
NG0589:1228: sgo yin rten gzugs rgyu gsum gnad //
NG0589:1229: nyi ma rten bzhi 'khor lo gnas //
NG0589:1230: der 'joms bcu drug las kyi tshad //
NG0589:1231: gsang ba ra sbyangs grangs med lam //
NG0589:1232: gsum gnas bsgrod pa rten dgu 'pho //
NG0589:1233: snying po srog sdud bcud la dbab //
NG0589:1234: sbyor ba gnyis kyis mnan par bya //
NG0589:1236: zla ba mar gyi ngo dag la //
NG0589:1239: dus ni 'brug sgra tshub ma la //
NG0589:1240: gsad pa'i las sogs drag po shis //
NG0589:1241: thabs kyi rlung rgyu drag po'i me //
NG0589:1242: nam dang nyi ma'i gung la ni //
NG0589:1243: brdeg dang sreg pa la sogs 'grub //
NG0589:1244: 'khor lo drag tu bskor ba'i tshe //
NG0589:1245: gshin rje'i 'khor rnams dbang sdud cing *//
NG0589:1246: spyi rgyug sngags kyis bar bar brab //
NG0589:1247: gshin rje dpa' bo mkha' 'gro la //
NG0589:1248: mi yi sha khrag rkang dang tshil //
NG0589:1249: rta dang ra yi sha rus khrag / de rnams snying dang 'bru rnams zas //
NG0589:1250: gtor mar byas te thod par dgang *//
NG0589:1251: snying khrag chang sbyar argam sbreng *//
NG0589:1252: gsur chen dud pa rgyun mi bcad //
NG0589:1253: rdza rnga brdung zhing gshin rje bod //
NG0589:1254: tshil chen mar me rtag tu btang *//
NG0589:1255: drag po 'khor lo rdzogs pa la //
NG0589:1256: mnan pa'i cho ga bshad bya ba //
NG0589:1257: 'khor lo thod 'khor nang du gzhug / tshas drag re thums byas nas ni //
NG0589:1258: srad bu nag pos rgya gram bcing *//
NG0589:1259: sman gtor bshams la gshin rje bod //
NG0589:1260: ma nyes dpang gzugs lha klu la //
NG0589:1261: bden pas bsgo zhing dmod bcol bya //
NG0589:1262: 'chi bdag rgyal po nyid la gtad //
NG0589:1263: dngos por ral pa tshar dgu pa //
NG0589:1264: gtad cing ri rab 'og tu gzhug / 'o na khung ro khung 'byung po'i srang *//
NG0589:1265: klu yi gnas su gtad par bya //
NG0589:1267: 'phags pa 'jam dpal gshin rje gshed 'khrul 'khor nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0589:1268: gsad pa'i 'khor lo bstan pa ste rtog pa dgu pa'o ///
NG0589:1269: / de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis las kyi 'khrul
NG0589:1270: 'khor nag po gshin rje gshed kyi mtshon cha phung
NG0589:1271: byed las kyi de kho na nyid dag gsungs so
NG0589:1272: // dkon mchog rgyal ba'i sku dgra la //
NG0589:1273: gshed bdag 'khor lo nag po bskor //
NG0589:1274: sbyor ba'i rgyal po 'bru bsdebs la //
NG0589:1275: kam pa ral gri so rir bcas //
NG0589:1276: me chu stobs dang rlung gi 'pho //
NG0589:1277: de yi sbyor ba 'di lta ste //
NG0589:1278: phyi nang gsang ba gnad dang gzer //
NG0589:1279: las kyi gcong chen 'bru btus la //
NG0589:1280: drag po'i 'khor lo bskor bar bya //
NG0589:1282: rdo rje'i phyogs su rim pas 'phangs //
NG0589:1284: rin po che nas dbus su sbyar //
NG0589:1285: nyi ma dang por shes par bya //
NG0589:1286: de bzhin rin po che nas kyang *//
NG0589:1287: dzi ha ka ma 'phreng ba ste //
NG0589:1289: nyi ma gnyis par shes par bya //
NG0589:1291: b+hu ra d+ha ra g+han da ste //
NG0589:1292: ral gri de bzhin dbus su'o //
NG0589:1295: tsakra ru par sbyar ba ni //
NG0589:1296: rdo rje sbyar ba dbus su 'gyur //
NG0589:1299: yang dag rdzogs pa'i rgyal pos bshad //
NG0589:1301: bcu gsum 'bru gnyis ldan pa ste //
NG0589:1302: las kyi bsnyen par bshad pa ste //
NG0589:1304: mu la nas ni rdo rje phyogs //
NG0589:1307: pad+ma rin po che sbyar te //
NG0589:1309: 'jigs byed rgyal po ya mas bshad //
NG0589:1311: thod mar dbus nas mgo drangs te //
NG0589:1312: rlung dang sa ste sgra dang reg / nam mkha' me dang yid dang sna //
NG0589:1313: mchu dang lce dang rna ba lus //
NG0589:1314: dus dang dri dang ro dang ni //
NG0589:1315: lta byed dang ni gzugs su sdebs //
NG0589:1317: de bzhin rlung dang sgra dang reg / nam mkha' dang ni sa ru sbyar //
NG0589:1318: chu dang lce dang rna ba dang *//
NG0589:1319: lus dus dri dang ro dang mig / gzugs dang me dang yid dang sna //
NG0589:1321: rlung dang nam mkha' reg bya sa //
NG0589:1322: sgra dang lus dus dri dang ro //
NG0589:1323: mig dang gzugs med yid dang sna //
NG0589:1324: chu dang lce ru bsdebs pa ni //
NG0589:1325: khrul 'khor gsum par bsdebs pa yin //
NG0589:1326: rlung dang nam mkha' sa dang sgra //
NG0589:1327: reg bya ro dang lta byed dang *//
NG0589:1328: lus dang me dang yid dang ni //
NG0589:1329: sna dang mchu dang lce ru bsdeb //
NG0589:1330: rna ba lus dus dri ru sbyar //
NG0589:1332: ta pa la yi 'bru btus ni //
NG0589:1333: sbyor ba rin chen sngags de nyid //
NG0589:1334: bcu bdun sngags kyi sbyor ba cig / las dang
NG0589:1335: mthu dang 'dren pa cig / mtshan nyid 'joms dang
NG0589:1336: rgyud dang bkol // mchog tu 'gugs shing dmigs 'dzug pa'o //
NG0589:1338: dang po rdo rje phyogs dag nas //
NG0589:1339: rlung nag me yi bar du bdun //
NG0589:1341: rims kyis sbyar ba dang po bzhin //
NG0589:1342: sa dang rlung ste me nas sa //
NG0589:1343: yid nas mer sbyar sna nas yid //
NG0589:1344: chu nas snas sbyar sgra dang chu //
NG0589:1345: rin po che yi phyogs dag nas //
NG0589:1346: rlung dang reg bya sgra dang rlung *//
NG0589:1347: chu sgra chu dang me ru bsdebs //
NG0589:1348: rna ba dag dang lce dang lus //
NG0589:1349: rna ba reg bya lus byar bsdeb //
NG0589:1350: pad+ma'i phyogs nas rlung dang mkha' //
NG0589:1351: reg bya rlung ste lus dang reg / dus dang lus te dri dang dus //
NG0589:1352: ro nas dri sbyar nam mkha' ro //
NG0589:1353: ral gri phyogs nas rlung dang sa //
NG0589:1354: nam mkha' rlung dang ro dam mkha' //
NG0589:1355: mig dang ro ste gzugs tsa ka kru //
NG0589:1356: me dang gzugs te sa dang me //
NG0589:1357: 'phreng sngags bdun po gshed chen rgyal //
NG0589:1358: 'gugs dang las la nye sbyar ba //
NG0589:1359: u mi ta dang 'dra ba yi //
NG0589:1360: drag sngags bcu gnyis brgyad yin te //
NG0589:1361: rjes su mthun pa'i rkyen sngags kyis //
NG0589:1362: nye bar sbyar na las kun byed //
NG0589:1363: grong khyar zad dang dkrugs pa'o //
NG0589:1364: las kyi rgyal po rdzogs byed yin //
NG0589:1365: de nas gzhan yang bshad bya ba //
NG0589:1366: rin chen drag po stobs kyi 'bru //
NG0589:1367: rdo rje yag sha ngar blud pa //
NG0589:1368: rdo rje drag po me yi sngags //
NG0589:1369: stag mo'i mchong ba'i stabs tshul gyis //
NG0589:1370: gzugs brgyab mi 'chor chu srin ltar //
NG0589:1372: phyogs nas phyogs mchongs phyogs bzhir dril //
NG0589:1375: rim gyis bskor ba drag po'i 'bru //
NG0589:1376: sdebs ni sbyor ba 'di nyid de //
NG0589:1377: bya rnan dang ni b+ha b+ha ste //
NG0589:1378: rgyab tu bi ya ka nyid do //
NG0589:1380: ho pan ta dang pa ne dang *//
NG0589:1382: d+hu ra d+ha ru tsa ta m+mu //
NG0589:1384: tsag kru dang ni jiyu ha dang *//
NG0589:1385: ru pa dang ni ka mar sbyar //
NG0589:1386: sdebs kyi sbyor ba dang por bshad //
NG0589:1388: b+ha b+ha b+h+ya ya ka dag dang *//
NG0589:1390: hopan ta dang pa ni dang *//
NG0589:1391: tsag kru dz+hu+i ha ru pa'o //
NG0589:1393: d+hu ra b+ha ru na sa dang *//
NG0589:1394: g+han d+ha bsdebs pa gnyis pa yi //
NG0589:1395: bya rnan b+h+ya ya b+ha b+ha dang *//
NG0589:1396: pra pa ti ak+sha pa ni dang *//
NG0589:1397: hol pan ta dang ak+she dang *//
NG0589:1398: kaa ni tan dang tsit+ta m+mu //
NG0589:1399: d+hu ra b+ha ru nas dang *//
NG0589:1401: ka ma ru pa sdebs pa ni //
NG0589:1402: gsum pa'i sbyor bar yang dag go / bya rnan ak+sha prap+ti dang *//
NG0589:1403: b+h+ya ya ka dang b+ha b+ha'o //
NG0589:1404: kaa ni tan dang ag ne dang *//
NG0589:1405: pa ni dang ni ho pan dang *//
NG0589:1406: dzu ha tsakru ka ma dang *//
NG0589:1407: ru pa b+hu ra ta ru dang *//
NG0589:1409: na sa sbyar ba bzhi pa ste //
NG0589:1410: drag po'i sbyor ba rim pa'o //
NG0589:1411: de dag rnal ma'i sbyor ba ste //
NG0589:1412: de bzhin g.yas su bgrod pa ni //
NG0589:1413: dbus su rta lang 'gros thabs kyis //
NG0589:1414: mgo gcig rim gyis 'phen par sbyar //
NG0589:1415: rdo rje gsang ba mchog nyid de //
NG0589:1416: stag gis mchongs pa'i sbyor ba nyid //
NG0589:1418: gsang pa sngags kyi bcud len pa //
NG0589:1419: thar pa'i thar pa ma lus 'joms //
NG0589:1420: nag po 'bru thus bdud kyi tshig / drag po
NG0589:1421: sdud pa sbyor ba'i mchog / yan lag ldan pas
NG0589:1422: ma lus bskyod // rdo rje rnon po'i 'khrul 'khor 'di //
NG0589:1423: gnod sbyin srin po'i 'khor lo yin //
NG0589:1424: drag po gshed kyi mtshon cha ste //
NG0589:1425: rin chen yi ge gser gyi 'bru //
NG0589:1426: dbus kyi gling bu re cha yi //
NG0589:1428: rdo rje'i ngar blud ur mo'i thog / bsdebs pas rgyal po'i las 'grub pa'o //
NG0589:1429: rlung dang sa sgra reg bya mkha' //
NG0589:1430: gnyis pa rlung sgra reg bya dang *//
NG0589:1431: nam mkha' dang ni sa ru sbyar //
NG0589:1432: gsum pa rlung dang reg bya mkha' //
NG0589:1433: sa dang sgra nyid sbyar ba'o //
NG0589:1434: bzhi pa rlung dang nam mkha' sa //
NG0589:1435: sgra dang reg bya sbyor ba'o //
NG0589:1436: nyi ma bzhi bsdebs mtshan mo yang *//
NG0589:1437: nam mkha' reg bya sgra dang sa //
NG0589:1438: rlung dang sbyar ba dang po yin //
NG0589:1439: gnyis dang gsum dang bzhi pa drag / rjes su mthun pa mtshan sngags te //
NG0589:1440: dbus kyi stag chen mjug sdum gyi //
NG0589:1441: gshed bzhis bsad pa'i sbyor bar bshad //
NG0589:1442: rten drug gnas la gdon bya ba //
NG0589:1443: thog mar 'bru gnyis dor byas nas //
NG0589:1444: rdo rje phyogs nas me dang yid //
NG0589:1445: sna dang chu dang sgra dang rlung *//
NG0589:1446: de bzhin rin chen chu dang lce //
NG0589:1447: rna ba lus dang reg bya rlung *//
NG0589:1448: pad+ma'i lus dang dus dang dri //
NG0589:1449: ro dang nam mkha' rlung dang sbyar //
NG0589:1450: ral gri ro dang lta byed @#//
NG0589:1452: gzugs dang sa dang rlung du sbyar //
NG0589:1453: mtshams su 'dod pa'i a mu ka / rdzogs pa sbyor ba bzhi nyid do //
NG0589:1454: phung po gnad dang 'byung ba lnga //
NG0589:1455: dang po lta byed sna dang chu //
NG0589:1456: de bzhin sgra dang ro la sbyar //
NG0589:1457: lce dang rna ba lus reg rlung *//
NG0589:1458: gzugs ngad me ro nam mkha' rlung *//
NG0589:1459: dmigs dus me sa rlung du sbyar //
NG0589:1460: phung po lnga yi rten bcom nas //
NG0589:1461: bde ba'i gnas dang sbyar bar bya //
NG0589:1462: dbus kyi 'bru lnga ru bzhi la //
NG0589:1463: 'phen byed rdo rje rin chen dbus //
NG0589:1464: rjes su rdo rje sbyar bar bya //
NG0589:1465: rlung dang rin chen pad+ma dbus //
NG0589:1466: mtha' ru rin po che la sbyar //
NG0589:1467: rlung dang pad+ma nam mkha' dbus //
NG0589:1468: mtha' ru pad+ma de bzhin no //
NG0589:1469: rlung dang nam mkha' sa dang dbus //
NG0589:1470: mtha' ru mkha' sbyar 'dod pa gzhug / chags sdang 'joms pa'i 'khrul 'khor yin //
NG0589:1471: dbus kyi 'bru lnga mu la ste //
NG0589:1472: de bzhin rdo rje rin chen pad //
NG0589:1473: dbus kyi 'bru sbyar 'dod pa gzhug / de bzhin rin chen pad+ma dang *//
NG0589:1474: ral gri sbyar ba dbus su 'gyur //
NG0589:1475: de bzhin pad+ma ral gri dang *//
NG0589:1476: rdo rje sa sbyar dbus su 'o //
NG0589:1477: de bzhin ral gri rdo rje dang *//
NG0589:1478: rin po che dang sbyar dbus su'o //
NG0589:1481: dbus nas mtha' ru 'bru deng de //
NG0589:1482: de bzhin mu la'i steng du mchongs //
NG0589:1483: dbus nas rdo rje dri dang rlung *//
NG0589:1484: de bzhin rin chen chu dang rlung *//
NG0589:1485: dbus kyi pad+ma lus dang rlung *//
NG0589:1486: de bzhin ral gri ro dang rlung *//
NG0589:1487: sgo bzhi las kyi rlung 'khor te //
NG0589:1488: mu khyud dang po'i sbyor ba dag / 'bru bzhi la yang de bzhin te //
NG0589:1489: rgyu bzhi nad bslang 'khrug pa yin //
NG0589:1491: rtsa gsum gnas dang rten bzhi gsum //
NG0589:1492: 'joms byed drag po'i yi ge ste //
NG0589:1494: me dang sa ste chu dang sgra //
NG0589:1495: lus dang reg bya ro dang mkha' //
NG0589:1497: rlung nag rdo rje pad+ma dang *//
NG0589:1498: de bzhin rin chen nam mkha' ste //
NG0589:1499: rjes su pad+ma rdo rje dang *//
NG0589:1500: de dag nam mkha' rin po che //
NG0589:1502: shes pa dang dwangs snyigs 'byed pa ni //
NG0589:1503: rdo rje rin chen pad+ma dang *//
NG0589:1504: ral gri bzhi yi mu lar sbyar //
NG0589:1505: phyag rgya bde chen lus nyid las //
NG0589:1506: yan lag sbyor ba rkyen rnams mdzes //
NG0589:1507: mtshon cha'i rgyal po nor bu'i 'bru //
NG0589:1508: bsnyen pa rgyun dang 'khor lo dang *//

NG0589:1517: gnad kyi mtshan nyid mtshon cha yin //
NG0589:1518: rtsa bzhir 'byung ba'i gnad dgu dbab //

NG0589:1523: spyi gcod mtshon cha spu gri med //

NG0589:1525: rkyen dgus phul la rta dgus 'phang *//
NG0589:1526: sgo dgu phye la gnad dgu dbab //
NG0589:1527: drag po sngags kyi 'khor lo nyid //
NG0589:1528: rtsa bar bcas pa'i lo ma can //
NG0589:1529: snying po mchog las yan lag rdzogs //
NG0589:1530: gsum dang bzhi lnga drug dang bdun //
NG0589:1531: brgyad dang dgu dang bcu bcu gcig / bcu gnyis la sogs du mar 'gyur //

NG0589:1535: 'phags pa 'jam dpal gshin rje gshed 'khrul 'khor nag po'i sngags rgyud las /
NG0589:1536: 'khrul 'khor sdebs kyi le'u ste rtog pa bcu pa'o
NG0589:1537: // // de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis 'khor lo
NG0589:1538: rang gnas kyi don zhes bya ba 'di dag gsungs
NG0589:1539: so // bsnyen pa'i dkyil 'khor phyi bsgrub ste //

NG0589:1545: phyi rim rtsa brgyad 'brel pa bzhi //
NG0589:1546: bdud sgo bzhi dang ldan pa la //

NG0589:1549: dbus su gshin rje gshed kyi sku //

NG0589:1551: dwangs ma bzhi yi si ra la //

NG0589:1553: rtsa bran brgyad dang yul bzhi la //

NG0589:1555: gsal rdzogs dbang bskur byin gyis brlab //
NG0589:1556: rang rgyud yid 'ong mchod rgyun brlan //
NG0589:1557: thugs kha'i sa bon ring du bskul //

NG0589:1564: lcang lor bdud rtsi bcud ri lu //
NG0589:1565: gling bzhi sku bris steng nas dgab //
NG0589:1566: 'od sgra dri dang gzugs mthong nas //
NG0589:1567: dngos grub chen po blang bar bya //
NG0589:1568: sku gsung rdo rje'i dngos grub sdu //

NG0589:1573: byin brlabs sna tshogs gang brtsams 'grub //
NG0589:1574: rgyal ba'i snying po 'khor lor bshad //

NG0589:1578: sku gsung thugs dang rigs lngar rdzogs //

NG0589:1584: sku che yan lag yum 'khyud pa //
NG0589:1587: bdud bzhi rtog tshogs gshed bzhi rigs //

NG0589:1622: srid gsum dgra yi shes rgyud gnas //

NG0589:1629: lha lnga sprad pa'i rdzas dud bdug / las gnyis ra la bzhi dbye ba bcu //

NG0589:1643: lus kyi dran pa nyams te 'gyur //
NG0589:1644: gnyis pa me yi rtsa srog gcod //

NG0589:1652: bzhi pa rlung gi rtsa bcad nas //

NG0589:1654: phyi yi rlung 'gags sgra nang rgyu //
NG0589:1657: dwangs ma skye med thig ler bsgral //
NG0589:1658: snyigs ma nri dang bcas pa bzhi //
NG0589:1660: sngags kyi pho nyas sha za bskul //
NG0589:1661: brnag pa'i lha dang srungs ma dral //

NG0589:1698: gsungs so // las kyi rgyal po 'khrul 'khor 'di //

NG0589:1722: dgos pa'i don chen gang la yang *//

NG0589:1726: dngos grub thob dang bsnyen pa rdzogs //
NG0589:1727: des ni drag po 'khor lo bskor //

NG0589:1729: dur khrod chu gling gnyen ra'i shing *//
NG0589:1730: bde ba'i gnas mchog ya ma'i gling *//
NG0589:1731: nag po dug gi snying po dang *//

NG0589:1735: srid pa gsum yang de na gnas //

NG0589:1743: phyi nang gsang ba nye bar gzung *//

NG0589:1745: bdud rtsi'i chu la khrus byed dang *//

NG0589:1764: bsgrub pa'i dngos gzhi dran pas gzung *//

NG0589:1776: yul la dmigs pa'i rten drug mthar //
NG0589:1777: drag po 'khor lo bskor ba dang *//
